---
layout: layouts/element.njk
title: "layout-badge"
description: "Small status indicators, labels, and counts. Perfect for tags, statuses, and notification counts."
elementName: layout-badge
category: custom
currentPath: /docs/elements/custom-elements/layout-badge/
permalink: /docs/elements/custom-elements/layout-badge/
---

{% set semanticColorsCode %}<layout-badge>Default</layout-badge>
<layout-badge data-color="primary">Primary</layout-badge>
<layout-badge data-color="success">Success</layout-badge>
<layout-badge data-color="warning">Warning</layout-badge>
<layout-badge data-color="error">Error</layout-badge>
<layout-badge data-color="info">Info</layout-badge>{% endset %}

{% set themeColorsCode %}<layout-badge data-color="brand">Brand</layout-badge>
<layout-badge data-color="secondary">Secondary</layout-badge>
<layout-badge data-color="accent">Accent</layout-badge>{% endset %}

{% set variantsCode %}<layout-badge data-variant="subtle" data-color="success">Subtle</layout-badge>
<layout-badge data-variant="outlined" data-color="error">Outlined</layout-badge>{% endset %}

{% set sizesCode %}<layout-badge data-size="sm">Small</layout-badge>
<layout-badge>Medium</layout-badge>
<layout-badge data-size="lg">Large</layout-badge>{% endset %}

<browser-window
    src="/docs/examples/demos/layout-badge-basic.html"
    url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/badge"
    title="Badge Demo"
    shadow>
  </browser-window>

  <section>
    <h2>Attributes</h2>
    <table class="props-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Attribute</th>
          <th>Values</th>
          <th>Default</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><code>data-color</code></td>
          <td><code>primary</code>, <code>success</code>, <code>warning</code>, <code>error</code>, <code>info</code>, <code>brand</code>, <code>secondary</code>, <code>accent</code></td>
          <td>neutral gray</td>
          <td>Color scheme (semantic or theme-aware)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>data-variant</code></td>
          <td><code>subtle</code>, <code>outlined</code></td>
          <td>solid</td>
          <td>Visual style</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>data-size</code></td>
          <td><code>sm</code>, <code>lg</code></td>
          <td>medium</td>
          <td>Badge size</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><code>data-shape</code></td>
          <td><code>square</code></td>
          <td>pill</td>
          <td>Border radius style</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Colors</h2>

    <h3>Semantic Colors</h3>
    <p>Use semantic colors for status indicators that convey specific meaning. These colors remain consistent regardless of theme.</p>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/snippets/demos/layout-badge-semantic-colors.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/layout-badge/semantic-colors"
      title="Semantic color badges"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Semantic colors">{{ semanticColorsCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h3>Theme Colors</h3>
    <p>Use theme colors for decorative purposes like tags, labels, and categories. These colors adapt to the site's brand hues.</p>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/snippets/demos/layout-badge-theme-colors.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/layout-badge/theme-colors"
      title="Theme color badges"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Theme colors">{{ themeColorsCode | escape }}</code-block>

    <h4>When to use which?</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Semantic colors</strong> - Status indicators (success/error), system messages, anything where color conveys meaning</li>
      <li><strong>Theme colors</strong> - Tags, labels, categories, decorative badges where color is for visual variety</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Variants</h2>
    <p>Choose between solid (default), subtle, or outlined styles.</p>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/snippets/demos/layout-badge-variants.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/layout-badge/variants"
      title="Badge variant styles"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Badge variants">{{ variantsCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Sizes</h2>
    <p>Three sizes available for different contexts.</p>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/snippets/demos/layout-badge-sizes.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/layout-badge/sizes"
      title="Badge sizes"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" show-lines label="Badge sizes">{{ sizesCode | escape }}</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Usage Examples</h2>

    <h3>Status Indicators</h3>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/snippets/demos/layout-badge-status.html"
